definitions.definition: ( UK ) Abbreviation or diminutive for baronet , later replaced by Bt . It is a post-nominative title; the pre-nominative is Sir (e.g. Sir John Smith Bart.).

main_definition: ( UK ) Abbreviation or diminutive for baronet , later replaced by Bt . It is a post-nominative title; the pre-nominative is Sir (e.g. Sir John Smith Bart.).

definitions.definition: A diminutive of the male given name Bartholomew .
